<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV44">
<l>niṟamuyar kōlamum pērum muruvu mivaiyivaiyeṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṟamuyal ñāṉac camayikaḷ pēcilu maṅkaṅkellā</l>
<l>muṟavuyar ñāṉac cuṭarviḷak kāyniṉṟa taṉṟiyoṉṟum</l>
<l>peṟamuyaṉ ṟārillai yālempi rāṉṟaṉ perumaiyaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“[His] high beauty of colour, [his] names and [his] forms are all these”,</l>
<l>even if the sectarians, [their] knowledge pursuing virtue, say so, except that</l>
<l>it stands everywhere as a glowing lamp of knowledge high in love,</l>
<l>they won’t manage to obtain anything of our lord’s greatness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
